Rational surgical strategy in urgent non-gravidic metrorrhagia. The authors made an analysis of aspects of using the diagnostic and operative hysteroscopy in diagnosis and treatment of urgent nongravidary metarrhagias (UNM) under conditions of the department of urgent gynecology of the multiprophile hospital. The authors have analyzed the causes of the development of UNM, revealed high incidence of adenomyosis (44.3%).